@{FG TEXT}
  Please do, the future of CandyFactory depends on you. CandyFactory is
  my gift to the Amiga community, because I think the Amiga is a neat
  system and I like to go against the flow. But I easily get bored with
  making documentation and doing bugfixes, so let me know that you're
  interested in CandyFactory and I will continue improving it.

